shortName: EVOLUTION AB UNSP ADR EACH REPR
longBusinessSummary: Evolution AB (publ) develops, produces, markets, and licenses live casino solutions to gaming operators primarily in Europe and the United States. The company runs the game from a casino table, which is streamed in real time and end users make betting decisions on their devices, such as desktops, smartphones, tablets, etc. It also runs on-premise studios at land-based casinos in Belgium, Romania, the United Kingdom, and Spain. The company's portfolio of games primarily includes Live Roulette, Live Lighting Roulette, Live Dream Catcher, Monopoly Live, Live Blackjack, Live Infinite Balckjack, Live Baccarat, Live Dragon Tiger, Live Super Sic Bo, Live Football Studio, Live Casino Hold'em, Live Three Card Poker, Live Caribbean Stud Poker, Live Ultimate Texas Hold'em, and Live Texas Hold'em Bonus Poker. It operates approximately 550 tables. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
